Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:01.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:11.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 當貓耳是藤原書記時那四宮就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:15.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:17.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你帶來的時間原本就只有四宮與貓耳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:23.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,貓耳與少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,互惠共生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:33.10,Kaguya_zw,,0,0,0,,這世上存在著生來就注定相配的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三葉草和蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,鱷魚與蜂鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,牛油果與醬油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:40.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後便是…貓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大多數人類都喜愛貓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:48.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而後在此 有四宮輝夜這一容貌端莊的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:52.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩種存在的相適性在他眼中又是如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:56.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛死了
