Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎會真的需要Cosplay嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.00,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\c&H2F2C2D&\3c&HF0F0F0&\fad(150,0)}法國交換留學生歡迎會日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:35.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法國可是僅次於日本的Cosplay大國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Cosplay是不需要語言交流的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想要超越語言限制增進友誼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比這更好的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:45.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:48.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.99,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\an8\fs75\c&H0405BF&\3c&HF3F3EF&}Mariage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:52.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.84,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 一看四宮我的表情就僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看點正常的東西然後冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,表情好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,反應不大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我還是不太適合這類裝扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:17.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還是讓藤原同學那樣可愛的女孩子戴比較合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.33,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.59,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長你也乾脆一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:23.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼說呢 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太多餘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得那麼一針見血 你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不適合這種裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:36.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.17,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\an8\fs75\c&H0405BF&\3c&HF3F3EF&}Mariage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 明明會長只是戴上了貓耳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說別人 這對輝夜而言是最棒的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 嘴角上揚停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:58.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會暴露我覺得會長很可愛的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎 四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:01.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,技能「咬舌頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而這也做不到完美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還是留下了模稜兩可的笑意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮你這是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我的貓耳有什麼意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你的貓耳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可真適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:28.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,視人為螻蟻的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是我是最不適合貓耳的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學 給會長拍張照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:45.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我可得把會長的這個樣子永遠存留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:46.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是威脅的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她打算將來留下證據然後用來威脅我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行！
