Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.26,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 NG詞語遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NG詞語遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 以這個為例
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:17.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣寫下NG詞語然後遞給右邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後別看內容舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:23.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個詞語就是那個人不能說的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.13,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:27.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 沒辦法知道自己的NG詞語是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:30.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們開始正式遊戲吧
