Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有誰能比四宮在日式點心方面的造詣更深
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:58.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣效率更高罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就讓藤原書記不斷獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我再贏過四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.05,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H212222&\3c&HF3F3F3&\an7\bord3\fs80}Check it out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原書記絕對不會說這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個遊戲 我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,YO YO 那就開始吧 YO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原書記？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:28.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有玩著NG遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,卻用平時說話語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:33.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就換了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遺憾啊 Man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別看她 我沒這個打算
