Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 他剛才要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:15.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要睡了
