Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說澀谷站被淹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:41.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
