Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,校長下次請不要在快要開始了才通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:26.15,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\fs85\b1\pos(1373,886)}白銀御行想說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家玩得盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮會說法語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是很擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你好大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫白銀御行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是會長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:51.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是翻了翻應急手冊 臨時抱佛腳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Bonjour
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Merci beaucoup pour votreinvitation d' aujourd' hui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}非常感謝你今天的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,C' est nous qui vous remercions d'être venus d' aussi loin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}感謝你們的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:08.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Nous ferons toutnotre possiblepour que vous gardiez un souvenir impérissable durant votreséjour parmi nous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:08.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}在這期間 我們將盡力為您留下難忘的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Je vous remercie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:15.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,La pluparts des contenusjaponais sont focalisés surle marché domestique Le Japon n' a pas encoreétabli la fa?on de se promouvoir à I' étranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:15.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}日本的文化產物大都集中在國內市場 因此還沒建立起在國外推廣的途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Les prix montent en flèche à I' exportation,il y a aussi les problèmes des ventes au rabais des licences des images…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}出口價格暴漲 圖片許可證的折扣銷售也存在問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你也會說法語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因為媽媽以前是外交官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候就被灌輸了各國語言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:31.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不會說法語的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完全孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被發現只有我不會說法語的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日本學校的學生會長居然不會說法語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Comme c' est mignon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:56.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 對心臟太不友好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:03.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得為什麼我會突然委託你策劃派對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:08.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須要看透你的才能是否值得我將學園託付給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來才是真正的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:23.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要有顧慮 全力去進攻那個叫白銀御行的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法國學校學生會副會長 Beltoise Betsy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱作是「舔舐傷口的剃刀」的她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:35.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在她的毒舌下沒有人可以毫髮無損
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Bonjour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 hey
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:47.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy 剛見面就使出破顏拳級別的諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接著是如同同時侮辱父母和戀人般的挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:58.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:03.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是能讓六十多歲的男性痛哭流涕的人格否定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:07.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀御行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麼可怕的攻擊下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然還能露出這樣從容的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫的話應該早就敗下陣來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就像完全聽不懂她說的話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:26.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻擊居然沒有效 這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:31.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy向白銀發起了強烈的侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:47.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 你聽不懂日語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:21:01.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜向Betsy發起了電視台放送事故級別的恐嚇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:13.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 不是的 剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我 會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的女子高中生太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:27.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,交流戰 日本學校的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:36.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定很瞧不起我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了那麼不文雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這簡直就好像以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的法語是臨時抱佛腳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能聽懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不知道你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:59.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道你是在替我打抱不平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:10.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 會長的這點我很…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:16.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:20.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 這樣會更在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密就是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:23.59,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:25.07,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,不是法語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:26.24,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是拉丁語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:26.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日戰局 兩人均勝利
